Subject: Re: towing capacity

It's not only the engine that determines towing capacity.  Your brakes are
typically the limiting factor and also the clutch plays a part.  The owner's
manual for my 1969 Kombi rates its towing capacity at 1100 lbs. with a 100 lb.
tongue weight.

